      },
      "date": "2018-01-17 09:47:00.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n\"To me it makes sense to have archive id in the range [0...LL_HSM_MAX_ARCHIVE], 0 being a special value.\"\n\nThis is exactly what the patch is doing. Before, the range was in [0..LL_HSM_MAX_ARCHIVE - 1]\nand thus LL_HSM_MAX_ARCHIVE was not included.\n\nThis problem is also described at:\n\njira.hpdd.intel.com/browse/LU-10260, where is written:\n\"... the code limits ARCHIVE ID to less than 32.\"",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
