      "date": "2018-02-03 10:35:44.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nDo sites actually use a single copytool for multiple archives, or would it be better to register multiple copytools in that case (one per archive) so that we can increase the number of archives to 2^32 rather than only 32?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "e134c8f7f623c710b8afc96561ea55a4adb46b64",
