        "_account_id": 500,
        "name": "Thomas Stibor",
        "email": "t.stibor@gsi.de",
        "username": "tstibor"
      },
      "date": "2018-02-05 14:09:40.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nFrom my point of view max. 32 archive_id's is rather limited\nand it would be good to increase this number.\n\nWe plan at GSI with 4 archive_id's for each experiment (copytool and TSM Server) and sooner or later run into the max. 32 limit.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
